此案的更多详情尚未公布，就让我们继续观望与追踪，希望周渝民与妻子可以成功追回损失。周渝民夫妇买保险被诈骗775万，闺蜜诈骗手法遭曝光_保费_妻子_喻虹渊"},"attached_info":"Cj4IzP/k4YOHk9gmEAMaCDgzNjk5NjAzIL+6nZcGMAM4V0Amcgk1NDYzNzM5ODR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"13 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-68999b155a0ef5893bc20ddd459ea8c9_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"39_1659436169.001086","card_id":"Q_546510407","target":{"id":546510407,"title":"郭艾伦向辽宁队提出转会申请，如何看待他的这一选择？会带来什么影响？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/546510407","type":"question","created":1659405499,"answer_count":76,"follower_count":109,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1538,4196,4749,35691,38311],"comment_count":2,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"郭艾伦2日通过经纪团队向中国男篮职业联赛（CBA）新科冠军辽宁队提出了转会申请。 郭艾伦的经纪团队表示，明年男篮世界杯是中国男篮冲击巴黎奥运会的关键比赛，郭艾伦作为中国男篮的后场核心，为了提升综合能力，保持竞技状态，同时给自己更大的挑战，选择主动跳出舒适圈，有了转会的意向。 郭艾伦的经纪团队还没有透露其最终去向。同时，郭艾伦通过经纪团队对这些年辽宁队的培养、辽宁球迷对自己的支持和厚爱表达感谢。他表示，自己选择离开最终的目的也是为了有更好的发展。"},"attached_info":"Cj4IzP/k4YOHk9gmEAMaCDgzNzI5ODU5ILuJopcGMAI4bUAncgk1NDY1MTA0MDd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"13 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-1f5dee7ad4452b370b653d3cead1070e_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"40_1659436169.0021913","card_id":"Q_533518804","target":{"id":533518804,"title":"戴宗一小时速度也就是 20 km，为什么不骑马？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/533518804","type":"question","created":1652923061,"answer_count":71,"follower_count":195,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[4364,23152,156313],"comment_count":13,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IzP/k4YOHk9gmEAMaCDgwODQxMjQ0ILW1lpQGMA04wwFAKHIJNT